Task 1: Design Login UI

Task Name: Create Login Page Interface

Description:
Design and develop a responsive and user-friendly login page for the Ebook system. Implement input fields for email and password, validation messages, and navigation links for new users.

游릭 Task 2: Implement JWT Authentication API

Task Name: Develop JWT-Based Authentication API

Description:
Create secure API endpoints for user registration and login using JWT. Generate access tokens upon successful authentication and validate tokens for protected API routes.

游릭 Task 3: Token Management (Cookie & Storage)

Task Name: Configure Token Storage and Management

Description:
Implement secure storage of JWT tokens using HttpOnly cookies and local storage. Handle token creation, retrieval, expiration, and deletion during login and logout.

游릭 Task 4: Protect Web Routes Using Middleware

Task Name: Implement Route Protection with Middleware

Description:
Develop and configure custom middleware to restrict access to dashboard and ebook pages. Ensure only authenticated users can access protected routes.

游릭 Task 5: Protect API Routes Using JWT Middleware

Task Name: Secure API Endpoints with JWT Middleware

Description:
Apply JWT authentication middleware to API routes to validate user requests. Restrict sensitive operations such as upload, delete, and share generation to authorized users.

游릭 Task 6: Implement Logout and Session Handling

Task Name: Develop Secure Logout and Session Management

Description:
Implement logout functionality to invalidate JWT tokens, clear cookies and local storage, and terminate active sessions securely.

游릭 Task 7: Prevent Unauthorized Access via Browser Navigation

Task Name: Disable Back Button and Cache Access

Description:
Configure cache-control headers and middleware to prevent access to protected pages using browser back and forward buttons after logout.

游릭 Task 8: Role-Based Access Control (Admin)

Task Name: Implement Admin Access Control

Description:
Restrict administrative features such as ebook upload, deletion, and share link generation using role-based authorization middleware.

游릭 Task 9: Implement Client-Side Authentication Guard

Task Name: Develop Frontend Authentication Guard

Description:
Add JavaScript-based authentication checks to verify token availability and validity before allowing access to protected pages and actions.

游릭 Task 10: Testing and Security Validation

Task Name: Perform Authentication Testing and Security Review

Description:
Test all authentication scenarios including login, logout, token expiration, unauthorized access, and error handling. Validate system security against common vulnerabilities.


